OL,3,CSocial care services to be impacted by
OL,4,C'unprecedented' financial pressures
OL,6,FHealth and social care services in
OL,7,FDumfries and Galloway "are likely to
OL,8,Fbe impacted" by a financial deficit,
OL,9,Faccording to healthcare bosses.
OL,11,FThe region's Integration Joint Board
OL,12,F(IJB) is facing a funding shortfall of
OL,13,Fnearly #58 million this financial
OL,14,Fyear. More than #25 million in savings
OL,15,Fhave already been identified, but this
OL,16,Fstill leaves a gap of #32.7 million.
OL,18,FOfficials have warned that difficult
OL,19,Fchoices could lie ahead as a result of
OL,20,Fthe "unprecedented" financial
OL,21,Fpressures.
