OL,3,CSocial care services to be impacted by
OL,4,C'unprecedented' financial pressures
OL,6,FInterim Chief Finance Officer Mathew
OL,7,FCrosby, of the Dumfries and Galloway
OL,8,FHealth and Social Care Partnership,
OL,9,Fsaid: "It is the most difficult
OL,10,Ffinancial position the IJB has
OL,11,Fencountered. Even with a very
OL,12,Fambitious savings programme, we are
OL,13,Fleft with a funding gap that threatens
OL,14,Fthe stability of essential services.
OL,16,F"We've worked hard to identify savings
OL,17,Fand drive efficiencies, but the
OL,18,Fpressures around staffing,
OL,19,Fprescribing, and care provision are
OL,20,Ffar beyond anything that can be solved
OL,21,Fthrough marginal cuts."
