OL,3,CSocial care services to be impacted by
OL,4,C'unprecedented' financial pressures
OL,6,FBoth health and social care services
OL,7,Fare being asked to deliver further
OL,8,Fsavings with #18.2 million coming from
OL,9,Fwithin the NHS and #12.5 million from
OL,10,Fadult social care through a range of
OL,11,Fmeasures including medicines
OL,12,Foptimisation, contract reviews, energy
OL,13,Fefficiency work, and new models of
OL,14,Fcare.
OL,16,FHowever, officials have warned that
OL,17,Fthis will inevitably have consequences
OL,18,Ffor the way services are delivered.
