OL,3,CSocial care services to be impacted by
OL,4,C'unprecedented' financial pressures
OL,6,FChief Officer of the Health and Social
OL,7,FCare Partnership Nicole Hamlet said:
OL,8,F"Our absolute priority is to sustain
OL,9,Fessential services.
OL,11,F"However, we need to be honest that
OL,12,Fthe scale of the financial challenge
OL,13,Fmeans we will not be able to provide
OL,14,Feverything that people might want or,
OL,15,Fin some cases, might previously have
OL,16,Fbeen entitled to. We are having to
OL,17,Ffocus on critical care and essential
OL,18,Fsupports."
