OL,6,FChair of the IJB Kim Dams added:
OL,7,F"We're in a very serious position, and
OL,8,Fwe must be realistic about the scale
OL,9,Fof the challenge.
OL,11,F"Our responsibility is to protect
OL,12,Fvital services while making sure they
OL,13,Fare financially sustainable. That will
OL,14,Fmean some difficult decisions, but
OL,15,Falso close collaboration right across
OL,16,Four health and care system.
