OL,6,F"We're keen to ensure that all
OL,7,Fstakeholders are aware of this
OL,8,Fsituation, and would ask them to lend
OL,9,Fas much understanding and support as
OL,10,Fpossible as we take the tough but
OL,11,Fnecessary decisions required to
OL,12,Fsafeguard critical services and ensure
OL,13,Fthe long-term sustainability of health
OL,14,Fand social care in our region."
